    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "You may want to try [rlipython](https://testpypi.python.org/pypi/rlipython) for use in emacs. We've switched to a new terminal interface library called prompt_toolkit, but unfortunately it doesn't play well with emacs 'inferior shell' mode. `--simple-prompt` turns it off, but as you found, that means that various features that depend on it no longer work."
